# UI Handoff Contract — VibeStack UI → Backend

## UI Location
- UI lives in /ui
- Preserve styling and layout exactly as generated by AI Studio.

## API Contract
GET /api/updates
query params: query, source_type, source_name, tag, sort(new|score), page, pageSize

Response:
{
  "items": [{ id, source_name, source_type, title, url, published_at, short_description, tags, internal_score }],
  "page": number,
  "pageSize": number,
  "total": number
}

## Non-negotiables
- Locked schema only (updates, newsletter_sends)
- Deterministic scoring; no LLM in ingestion
- No auth / user accounts
- Ingestion via cron every 8 hours
- Newsletter weekly Top 5

## Success
- UI reads from /api/updates (real Postgres data)
- Filters + pagination work
